OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will start with
OL,6,Fbright spells and scattered rather
OL,7,Fblustery showers. It should become
OL,8,Fmostly fine for a while heading into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, though thicker cloud
OL,10,Fand rain will arrive from the
OL,11,Fsouthwest later. Mild, though
OL,12,Fremaining breezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FThe evening will be cloudy
OL,15,Fand wet with some rain and fog patches
OL,16,Faffecting the region. The rain will
OL,17,Fslowly peter out overnight, though
OL,18,Fstaying rather cloudy. Mild, though
OL,19,Fbreezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
