OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FTuesday morning looks cloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy with patchy light rain,
OL,7,Fchiefly in the west. Some brighter
OL,8,Fspells are possible later, especially
OL,9,Fin the east where it will become very
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FAnother very mild, though fairly
OL,14,Fcloudy day on Wednesday with some rain
OL,15,Fin the west. Cooling down thereafter
OL,16,Fand turning more unsettled with rain
OL,17,Fand strong winds possible at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
